{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fugue Shot blends the strategic depth of a roguelike with the creative problem-solving of a physics puzzler. Each run presents a series of unique dreamscapes, filled with increasingly difficult puzzles and randomized encounters meant to  test your abilities to their limit. Strategic thinking and skillful execution are key to overcoming the ever-shifting landscape of this liminal and surreal world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Build Your Own Solutions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Set up your playfield, test different ideas, and interact with a satisfying physics engine to master constantly changing puzzles and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538440/extras/ScreenRecording2025-02-03at1.25.25AM-ezgif.com-optimize__1_.gif?t=1740101873\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Power Up Your Run</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from dozens of unique items to impact your gameplay and warp your playstyle.\u00a0Discover powerful synergies to create truly unique builds, allowing for emergent gameplay and a constantly shifting experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538440/extras/ScreenRecording2025-02-03at1.31.09AM-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1740101873\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Enjoy a Eerily Beautiful World</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stunning pixel art and visual effects compliment a haunting and meditative soundtrack to create a surreal, dream-like atmosphere that you can lose yourself in for hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538440/extras/ScreenRecording2025-02-03at1.13.29AM-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converte